    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It's in really solid shape\u2014super clean inside and runs like a dream. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and it\u2019s totally ready for its next adventure with you! It's been perfect for my daily commutes and weekend getaways, and I know you'll love it just as much as I have. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
