    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2017 Ford Focus RS is a mechanically sound example of the Blue Oval\u2019s rally-bred hot hatch. Under the hood, the 2.3L EcoBoost inline-four utilizes a twin-scroll turbocharger to deliver linear power through a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. The standout GKN Twin-ster AWD system provides active torque vectoring, ensuring neutral handling and high-speed stability. Equipped with the factory-spec Brembo four-piston front calipers and adjustable dampers, the chassis dynamics remain sharp and responsive. This unit has undergone the critical head gasket recall service and features forged alloy wheels. While it shows minor cosmetic indications of road use, the drivetrain remains tight, and the engine maintains excellent compression across all cylinders.",
