    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This 2018 BMW 540i xDrive is a prime example of a well-cared-for luxury sedan. Finished in a sophisticated Bluestone Metallic, the exterior retains a deep gloss, with only the minor road nicks one would expect from careful daily use. Inside, the Black Dakota leather remains supple and free of tears, and the cabin is a quiet sanctuary thanks to the meticulous upkeep of all seals and interior trim. Mechanically, this vehicle is robust; it has been serviced exclusively at certified dealerships, with a full log of preventative maintenance including a recent oil service, brake fluid flush, and a fresh set of premium all-season tires. The 3.0L turbocharged inline-six pulls smoothly, and the 8-speed transmission shifts imperceptibly. All electronics, from the gesture-control infotainment system to the heated seats and sunroof, function perfectly. While not a showroom-new 'mint' vehicle, this car represents a reliable, high-performing choice for the discerning driver who values documented mechanical integrity and a clean, professional presentation.",
      "price": 34900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
