      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, an exemplary choice for the discerning driver who prioritizes both performance and long-term value. This automobile has undergone a rigorous professional inspection to ensure mechanical integrity and aesthetic refinement. Featuring a clean provenance and a suite of sophisticated amenities, it offers a superior driving experience that distinguishes it from standard market offerings. We invite you to evaluate this distinguished vehicle, which stands as a testament to disciplined ownership and enduring quality.",
      "price": 34900.0,
