    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for this awesome ride. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really great shape, both inside and out! It runs smoothly and has been well-cared for, making it the perfect choice for anyone needing a dependable daily driver that still looks sharp on the road. I\u2019ve loved every mile in it, and I know you will too! Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come see it in person!",
      "price": 34500.0,
