    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 naturally aspirated 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile engagement, paired with a factory-spec limited-slip differential for optimal torque distribution. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive inspection of the rear subframe mounts and VANOS system adjustment to ensure structural and mechanical longevity. Riding on a well-sorted suspension with sharpened turn-in response, this chassis remains balanced and communicative. A driver-focused example with high mechanical integrity, ready for the twisties.",
